  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>An american style buffet breakfast is served each morning in the dining room and offers freshly baked pastries, breads, cold cuts, yogurts and fruit. All complimented by freshly brewed coffees and teas. </p>
<p>Dinner is four courses with a choice of dishes ranging from traditional Italian cuisine such as spaghetti alla vongole to European fusion dishes.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
