  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Continental Wellness &amp; Spa has it all– a prime lakefront position, superb facilities and excellent staff. It’s tucked away just outside the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/93a0ea3cd0334ca088eaf788bad0faba" href="/{localLink:umb://document/93a0ea3cd0334ca088eaf788bad0faba}" title="Sirmione">Sirmione</a>, which you can walk to in about five minutes.</p>
<h2>Peace &amp; quiet</h2>
<p>The location means it’s nice and peaceful so once you’ve spent some time in the hustle and bustle of the town you can head back here and chill out by the heated pool. The lake is just steps away and there’s a wooden jetty that gives easy access to the water.</p>
<h2>Traditional meets modern</h2>
<p>Inside you’ll find a mix of traditional and modern. The rooms are comfy and spacious with side views over the lake from the balcony. Dinner's a real highlight with plenty of choice on the half board menu – it changes every day so you can try lots of typical Italian food.</p>
<h2>Time to Relax</h2>
<p>Our favourite feature of the hotel is the spa – it’s modern and elegant and you'll feel instantly relaxed here. It’s open daily and free for guests so make sure you head there to check out the Finnish sauna, steam bath and chromo-therapy showers. You can access the outdoor pool straight from the spa so it’s easy to spend a whole day here.</p>]]></description>
