  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Superior Twin Rooms</strong> are about 20m² and can sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single sofa bed). They have partial views of the lake and a balcony. A family package is also available for these rooms, please call to enquire.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites </strong>are about 26m² and sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single sofa bed). They have a terrace with a side lake view and also overlook the pool. These rooms are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Rooms</strong> are around 20m² and sleep two people. They have a balcony with lovely lake views. These rooms are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms</strong> <strong>for sole use</strong> are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><em>Please request twin or double beds at the time of booking.</em></p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Bath or shower</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Tea &amp; coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Air conditioning</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Two chairs</li>
<li>Writing Desk</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Safe</li>
</ul>
<p>Cots are available for approx. €20 per day, payable locally</p>
<p><strong>Local fees &amp; taxes</strong></p>
<p>A tourist tax of approx. €2.80 per person per night is payable locally.</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
